snippet.title: Cursed Enigma : The Midnight Apartment - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST avaiable ON STEAM  !
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2803640/Cursed_Enigma__The_Midnight_Apartment/

Franco moves into an Italian townhouse, where an unsettling presence lead him to uncover dark truths about his new home. Dive into the mysterious events lurking behind the peaceful exterior of the building in the second episode of CURSED ENIGMA: The Midnight Apartment.
